me dans <strong>une taille supérieure<\/strong> à votre pointure habituelle ! <\/p><p>Entre <strong>doublure intérieure<\/strong> et <strong>fourrure confortable<\/strong>, <strong>90%<\/strong> de nos Payotins ont vu les choses en (plus) grand avec nos espa'chaussons.<\/p>","text_style":"body","text_column":1,"text_color":"#21306b","img_replacement":false,"text_alignment":"center"}}},"block_order":["heading_ymMHTe","text_tTPFTm"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/vache_94a02505-5615-44c3-a426-c065a51dddd8.webp","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","full_width":false,"side_side":false,"desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","no_color":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","background_color":"#ffffff","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"image_with_text_83F6pc":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_zhbNy4":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Mules, montantes : pointure supérieure, allure élégante","heading_size":"h2","heading_color":"#21306b","img_replacement":false,"heading_alignment":"left"}},"text_t9jwC8":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Friand du <strong>confort unique<\/strong> des chaussons mules ou montants ? On vous comprend ! Pour ces modèles, optez plutôt pour <strong>une taille supérieure<\/strong> à votre taille habituelle. Ainsi, vous compenserez le <strong>manque de couverture arrière<\/strong> pour les mules, et permettrez plus d'espace pour la <strong>doublure intérieure<\/strong> des montantes.<\/p><p>Là encore,<strong> 90%<\/strong> de nos clients ont suivi la voie du confort. <\/p>","text_style":"body","text_column":1,"text_color":"#21306b","img_replacement":false,"text_alignment":"left"}}},"block_order":["heading_zhbNy4","text_t9jwC8"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Samantha3_dccdfd5b-2ac3-4a7a-bdc3-269cf03878c7.webp","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_